name: Universe #292
description: Universe #292 - The universe called Krism was the top point of order in the most fun way possible. The people worked on it's world on all kinds of projects to be delivered to other universes, but lately things slowed down. Their inventions and productions could not reach as much of the universes they wished to reach. 292 saw this and their pure wishes and decided to help them. Now the people do what they do as 292 helps them carry their creations all around the void.
